HEADWORD: Slanderous
<hw>Slan"der*ous</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Given
or disposed to slander; uttering slander.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Slanderous</xex> tongue.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Embodying or containing slander; calumnious; <as>as,
<ex>slanderous</ex> words, speeches, or reports</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p>-- <wordforms><wf>Slan"der*ous*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Slan"der*ous*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Slang</ent>⟦br⟧
